Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shape
      • Vertex

  • public class Vertex
extends Shape
    This class's main purpose is to build objects that represent a vertex, or point, on a plane with given x and y coordinates. This class can be added to with ease in order to be used to implement 3D-shapes.
    Author:
    Teagen Kiel
